Package: my-daemon
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, systemd
Description: Sample systemd-managed daemon for APT packaging demonstration
 This package demonstrates how to bundle a systemd service in a Debian package.
 It installs a simple daemon binary and a systemd service unit that manages
 its lifecycle (start, stop, enable, disable).